data.description: MOTIVATED SELLERS. $1000 bonus to the buyers agent. Welcome to Whisper Valley, ranked Austin's 2022 master planned community of the year by Austin Business Journal! Every home here has solar panels and geothermal air conditioning. This charming and welcoming residence that epitomizes the quintessential Texas suburban lifestyle. Nestled in the heart of Manor, a growing and vibrant community just northeast of Austin, this address offers the perfect blend of tranquility and convenience. As you approach 16309 Fetching Ave, you'll be greeted by its attractive curb appeal. The manicured front yard and well-maintained exterior showcase pride of ownership. The warm, earthy tones of the facade and the inviting porch create a sense of homey comfort. Step inside, and you'll find a spacious and thoughtfully designed interior that boasts modern amenities and a functional layout. The open-concept living areas are ideal for both everyday living and entertaining. The kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring sleek countertops, ample cabinetry, and top-of-the-line appliances. The adjacent dining area is bathed in natural light, making it an inviting spot for family meals. This residence offers multiple bedrooms, including a spacious master suite that provides a private retreat. The additional bedrooms are versatile, making them suitable for family members, guests, or a home office. The backyard at 16309 Fetching Ave is a serene escape where you can unwind and soak up the Texas sunshine. This area provides a perfect backdrop for outdoor gatherings, barbecues, or simply enjoying a peaceful evening under the stars. Manor, Texas, is a community on the rise, and living at 16309 Fetching Ave means you'll have easy access to Austin which means you're never far from the vibrant cultural scene, dining options, and employment opportunities the city has to offer.
